msgid "Rotate and Shear"
msgstr "Gira i inclina"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/rotate_and_shear.rst:16
msgid ""
"This would appear to be the `Affine <https://www.mltframework.org/plugins/"
"FilterAffine/>`_ MLT filter as defined in :file:`rotation.xml` (:file:`/usr/"
"share/kdenlive/effects/`)."
msgstr ""
"Aquest semblaria ser el `filtre «Affine» <https://www.mltframework.org/"
"plugins/FilterAffine/>`_ del MLT, com es defineix a :file:`rotation.xml` (:"
"file:`/usr/share/kdenlive/effects/`)."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/rotate_and_shear.rst:18
msgid "Rotate clip in any 3 directions."
msgstr "Gira el clip en qualsevol de les tres direccions."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/rotate_and_shear.rst:20
msgid ""
"This screen shot shows settings for Rotate and Shear that can correct wide-"
"screen footage shot while holding the camera the wrong orientation."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta captura de pantalla mostra les opcions Gira i Inclina que poden "
"corregir el metratge d'amplada de la pantalla mentre manteniu la càmera amb "
"una orientació incorrecta."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/rotate_and_shear.rst:22
msgid ""
"Do a rotate X of 900 units (the units are in tenths of a degree). You can "
"also adjust the size with this effect."
msgstr ""
"Fa un gir X de 900 unitats (les unitats estan en dècimes de grau). Amb "
"aquest efecte també podreu ajustar la mida."

